<h2>2. What BattlePicks Is</h2>
<p>BattlePicks is a Daily Fantasy Sports ("DFS") platform that offers skill-based peer-to-peer prediction contests ("Contests"). Users compete against one another — not against BattlePicks — by selecting individual player statistical performance predictions ("Picks"). BattlePicks acts as a neutral platform facilitating Contests between Users and does not take positions against Users, set odds, or act as a bookmaker.</p>
<p>Contest outcomes are determined by the actual statistical performance of real athletes in real sporting events. BattlePicks charges a platform fee ("Rake") of 5% on each completed Contest, deducted from the prize pool.</p>
<p>All odds and statistical lines displayed on the platform are sourced from licensed third-party sportsbooks via The Odds API. BattlePicks does not create, modify, or set any odds or lines.</p>
